@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<section>
    <p>
        At <strong>EverCare Community</strong>, your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal information when you use our website and services.
    </p>

    <h3> Information We Collect</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, date of birth, and other contact or demographic information.</li>
        <li><strong>Medical Information:</strong> Health-related data provided by residents, caregivers, or doctors for care purposes.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you interact with our site, such as pages visited, time spent, and actions taken.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3> How We Use Your Information</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Provide personalized healthcare support and communication</li>
        <li>Facilitate registration and application processes</li>
        <li>Improve our website and services</li>
        <li>Maintain accurate records for appointments, care plans, and communication</li>
        <li>Comply with legal and regulatory requirements</li>
    </ul>

    <h3> Data Sharing and Disclosure</h3>
    <p>We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your information with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Authorized caregivers and doctors for care coordination</li>
        <li>Third-party service providers for hosting, analytics, and support (bound by confidentiality agreements)</li>
        <li>Authorities if legally required (e.g., to comply with a court order)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3> Data Security</h3>
    <p>We take appropriate measures to safeguard your information against unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. These include:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Encrypted storage and transmission</li>
        <li>Access control protocols</li>
        <li>Regular system updates and monitoring</li>
    </ul>

    <h3> Your Rights</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Access your personal data</li>
        <li>Request corrections or deletions</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
        <li>Lodge a complaint with a data protection authority</li>
    </ul>

    <h3> Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h3>
    <p>We may use cookies to enhance user experience and gather analytics. You can choose to disable cookies through your browser settings.</p>

    <h3> Updates to This Policy</h3>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be posted on this page with a revised effective date.</p>

    <h3>Contact Us</h3>
    <p>If you have questions or concerns about this policy, please contact us at:</p>
    <ul>

        <li>📧 <a href="mailto:support@evercarecommunity.org">support@evercarecommunity.org</a></li>
        <li>📞 (123) 456-7890</li>
    </ul>
</section>
